Package org.presentation.model.logging

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MessageMapper
    This interface should serve as object for conversion between some specific kind of Message or other similar object.
    MessageProducer
    Interface of MessageProducer, which every control, that wants to produce Message for user output, must implement.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DebugMsg
    Represents debug type of abstract class Message.
    ErrorMsg
    Represents error type of abstract class Message.
    InfoMsg
    Represents infomation type of abstract class Message.
    InvalidLinkMsg
    Represents invalid link type of abstract class Message, which extends class ErrorMsg for ResponseCode.
    Message
    Abstract class representing common composition of messages, which is used for representing all outputs from all controls.
    MessageLogger
    Class that represents logger for Message, which gathers messages from the resource.
    MessageLoggerContainer
    Class that represents united container for all MessageLogger.
    MsgLocation
    This class represents location of Message in page content.
    MsgReport
    This class represents generated MsgReport from all added MessageLogger given by resource name of control, they are related to and List of Message, that this control produced.
    ResponseCode
    Represents HTTP response code.
    WarningMsg
    Represents warning type of abstract class Message.
